    "description": "关于《苍穹乾坤》<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/ea4cf2de18a00b62020116859a4a768c.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/ea4cf2de18a00b62020116859a4a768c.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/ea4cf2de18a00b62020116859a4a768c.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《苍穹乾坤》是一款全新的解谜冒险游戏，由曾经推出大热游戏《神秘岛》和《神秘岛2：星空断层》(Riven)的同一家传奇游戏工作室打造。感受深邃的剧情叙述和世界构建特色，深入这个看似被遗弃的世界，了解它的故事，探索和解开三大独特领域的重重谜团…直至登峰造极！<br><br>探索世界<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/b0540a22cab8be15326b92b884d35e67.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/b0540a22cab8be15326b92b884d35e67.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/b0540a22cab8be15326b92b884d35e67.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>伴随独特的蒸汽朋克美学，《苍穹乾坤》邀你探索Cyan世界最擅长的传奇、深邃的构建体系。《苍穹乾坤》堪称一次精彩绝伦的视觉盛宴，处处都是摄人心魄的新景致。与此同时，《苍穹乾坤》的世界又让人感觉合情合理；仿佛它在构建时就蕴含着一个更大的意图… 正是这个意图，让你在游玩过程中愈发无法自拔。<br><br>解决难题<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/62377b8cb1974523c154eeebf4841e1d.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/62377b8cb1974523c154eeebf4841e1d.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/62377b8cb1974523c154eeebf4841e1d.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在探索过程中，你携带着一部名为“副手”的装置。此副手是你与《苍穹乾坤》各个领域中的各种装置交互的媒介。借助副手解决你遇到的难题，这将会为你带来前所未有的机会，一举解开这个地方所蕴藏的秘密。<br><br>发现故事<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/27e346fa32f59230d892e4420edb95bf.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/27e346fa32f59230d892e4420edb95bf.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/27e346fa32f59230d892e4420edb95bf.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《苍穹乾坤》中，你并非完全孑然一身。除了副手，你还有一个神秘的亡灵相伴左右——一个希望和你分享她自己的故事的亡灵。随着探索的深入，你将会面对三大领域，每个领域都有自己的秘密和谜团有待揭开。这些领域为何存在？一路相伴的先灵是否值得信任？<br><br>揭开谜团<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/9a7ce2211564f15e4f89557410a5f5bf.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/9a7ce2211564f15e4f89557410a5f5bf.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/9a7ce2211564f15e4f89557410a5f5bf.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《苍穹乾坤》的各个领域是被遗弃了吗？这些散布于整个世界中的巨大、神秘的机器是什么？它们有何用途？你在这个巨大的谜团中扮演着何种角色？游玩《苍穹乾坤》，依靠你自己的力量探索、发现、解谜并揭开谜团！<br><br>技术细节<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/f00edbfd80f87a5b0de11b77186f162c.poster.avif?t=1749770252\" width=620 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/f00edbfd80f87a5b0de11b77186f162c.webm?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/754890/extras/f00edbfd80f87a5b0de11b77186f162c.mp4?t=1749770252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i><strong>专为VR和2D显示环境打造</strong></i><br><br>《苍穹乾坤》同时支持2D和VR游玩。《苍穹乾坤》的VR体验包括“自由漫游”和“传送”模式。<br><br>不仅如此，《苍穹乾坤》还包含大量“舒适水平”特色功能，让新老VR用户都能乐在其中，其中包括可自主选择顺滑或分段转向、快速登上楼梯或梯子、垂直高度量化，以及更多其他精彩功能！",
